<plot>Faith &amp; Fear explores one of the darkest secrets of the 1970s and 80s -- the reported abandonment and abuse of children raised as Hare Krishnas. This documentary combines in-depth interviews with exclusive archival footage to explore the history of the Hare Krishna movement and the experiences of former members.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?187916</url></doc>
